(INDISTINCT CHATTER ON POLICE RADIO)

02:07.462 --> 02:11.216
MAN 1: Stop moving, please.
Stop moving.

02:13.802 --> 02:15.053
MAN 2: In the back.

02:19.891 --> 02:20.892
