02:22.311 --> 02:24.479
GIBSON: Some costume night or something.

02:27.232 --> 02:28.650
School fundraiser.

02:31.778 --> 02:33.488
Victim's on the back terrace.

02:33.947 --> 02:34.990
Q U I N LAN: Witnesses?

02:35.073 --> 02:37.743
GIBSON: Got plenty,
