was a nose for everybody else's business.

06:22.801 --> 06:23.927
Oh, my God.

06:24.010 --> 06:25.136
Believe me, I know.

06:27.597 --> 06:28.640
Um...

06:28.848 --> 06:30.642
Do you need a ride or something?

06:30.976 --> 06:32.269
I'm a stay-at-home mom myself,

06:32.352 --> 06:34.646
