is about $150,000.

06:59.838 --> 07:04.634
I work in community theater, 20 hours a week,
so I'm definitely an "under."

07:05.176 --> 07:06.970
- What do you do?
- Just bookkeeping.

07:07.053 --> 07:09.472
So most definitely an "under," too.

07:10.890 --> 07:13.727
When I grow up,
I'm gonna run a massive label.

07:15.020 --> 07:16.396
